WINDOWS:

install python 2.7
click on epimorphism.py or run with python 2.7 via a console

LINUX:

Dependencies - python2.7, distutils, PIL, freeglut, python-opengl

./epimorphism


OSX:





NEW APP:
 add $app object to config/applications.py
 add config/app/$app_default.app
 add config/state/$app_default.est
 add kernels/$app_kerenls.cl